snippet.title: Bay Tek Games- Connect Four (Deluxe)
snippet.description:
Coin-up with the classic board game, Connect 4 by Hasbro.

Step up to the player station and choose your checker. Play head-to-head or against the computer. Take turns dropping checkers in the grid to try to connect four-in-a-row.

Connect 4 offers great play-value and a chance to win big tickets in the bonus round!
